column5: any recent reports from the miles bay area ? thanks
By what I've seen on facebook last week must have been really good for pike muskie and walleye.I'll be up there the 8th-19th of august. but that don't help any today.
Walleye fishing has been ok. Not many big ones being caught, but lots of 14-17" fish. Musky and big pike have been very good! 3 - 50+" musky caught last week for us.
